            <title>[DERBY-1388] Integrate processing code of two writeScalarStream methods.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1388</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Reading the two of writeScalarStream methods in org.apache.derby.client.net.Request class,&lt;br/&gt;
I found that one is for InputStream and another is for Reader and &lt;br/&gt;
that they are independent methods.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think these two methods should share integrated method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
