                            <comment id="12415355" author="naka" created="Thu, 8 Jun 2006 21:47:02 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;My plan is &lt;br/&gt;
to call writeScalarStream method for InputStream, from that for Reader, &lt;br/&gt;
with parameter of InputStream object that contains Reader object passed to writeScalarStream method.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12415730" author="naka" created="Sun, 11 Jun 2006 12:37:33 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I read that Reader version of the method writeScalarStream encodes characters from Reader as UTF-16BE and send it to server.&lt;br/&gt;
Then, it would be possible to place InputStream of which source is the Reader.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12416209" author="naka" created="Wed, 14 Jun 2006 23:16:24 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Description of patch :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Two writeScalarStream method in Request class are integrated after this patch.&lt;br/&gt;
     After the patch,method for Reader calls method for InputStream.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Test of this patch :&lt;/p&gt;
